title: PATATYI Ukrainian
description:
DVDrip Ukrainian 2 channels sound and subtitles.

For teaching Ukrainian to diaspora children only. Any other use violates my purpose which is devoid of any malicious intent. If you live in Ukraine, buy it. As I did.

If you object to the existence of this torrent, please consider helping make Ukrainian-language materials commercially available in countries where there are more than a million Ukrainians who currently only have access to English or Russian versions. That would be (in decreasing order) Ukraine(!) Russia, Canada and the United States.
